'''Abu Nuwas al-Ḥasan ben Hani Al-Ḥakami''' (ilul ahat deg [[Baṣra]] neɣ deg [[Dimecq]] deg [[756]] – yemmut deg [[814]]), d yiwen seg yimedyazen imeqranen akk ay yessefran s taɛṛabt takelsakt, yerna yella yessefruy, tikkal, ula s tfarsit.<ref>Esat Ayyıldız. [https://dergipark.org.tr/tr/download/article-file/1312336 "Ebû Nuvâs’ın Şarap (Hamriyyât) Şiirleri"]. Bozok Üniversitesi İlahiyat Fakültesi Dergisi 18 / 18 (2020): 147-173.</ref> 

Baba-s d Aɛṛab, ma d yemma-s d Tafarsit. Abu Nuwas yella yessen ad yessefru deg waṭas n tewsatin (genres) n tmedyazt taɛṛabt, yerna yeqqel mechuṛ ladɣa imi ay d-yettwabder deg [[Adlis n Wagim Waḍan|Wedlis n Wagim Waḍan]] ed [[Yiwen Yiḍ]].

